tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"有啲貓糧係for 戶外型多活動嘅貓 <br />\n熱量會比普通糧多<br />\n或者好似比母貓糧都得"},{"pid":"9836133225ff7d69731d5e4e1d5eabd21ee1fd2c","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲貓糧係for 戶外型多活動嘅貓 <br />\n熱量會比普通糧多<br />\n或者好似比母貓糧都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵搵資料先"},{"pid":"15e1e0fbfed85eeba99cd76b436cf34f6b9052f2","tid":217191,"uid":48946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<br />\n要比多d野食佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法令佢食多d野</blockquote><br />\n放長糧都咁瘦？<br />\n喂開咩糧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg&h=99604aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4BC5BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4BC5BD.jpg&h=c337a555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02384Ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02384Ah.jpg&h=c3ac68ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不定期換口味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂喂<br />\n貓既糧唔可以成日換<br />\n我諗你隻貓屙 係因為你咁樣轉糧<br />\n通常係食死一隻 有事/想轉糧先溝糧換<br />\n唔係咁樣一個月 兩個月咁轉黎轉去"},{"pid":"9cdd896797bada7fce8ed06641823c0a11934a85","tid":217191,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"有無試過蒸下雞俾佢食啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要肥返d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b763ee99bcfdae8f0f330d9d67b778540c979b74","tid":217191,"uid":88371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無計<br />\n<br />\n佢唔多食野<br />\n其他香口野佢會食到肚all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食得急又會嘔</blockquote><br />\n主人腸胃麻麻地喎<br />\n有冇試過餵貓草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc350ce7206c99741c363abcb75b9b55d6d31538","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無計<br />\n<br />\n佢唔多食野<br />\n其他香口野佢會食到肚all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食得急又會嘔</blockquote><br />\n主人腸胃麻麻地喎<br />\n有冇試過餵貓草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢食完一2啖然後推跌個貓草落地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔太喜愛"},{"pid":"820d30df832aa439d49055103539bc624d47631f","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"*下"},{"pid":"75ed991439eb4c9adaf50897e41c939de07555f7","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無試過蒸下雞俾佢食啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要肥返d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就咁係街市超市買凍鮮，再唔落油煮熟俾佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb643b714a78a31f568674708ca9d591c21f9081","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<br />\n要比多d野食佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法令佢食多d野</blockquote><br />\n放長糧都咁瘦？<br />\n喂開咩糧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg&h=99604aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4BC5BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4BC5BD.jpg&h=c337a555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02384Ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02384Ah.jpg&h=c3ac68ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不定期換口味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂喂<br />\n貓既糧唔可以成日換<br />\n我諗你隻貓屙 係因為你咁樣轉糧<br />\n通常係食死一隻 有事/想轉糧先溝糧換<br />\n唔係咁樣一個月 兩個月咁轉黎轉去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一牌子，轉味都唔好？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到佢都覺得慘<br />\n食死一隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bc6dab2440e07979e93e294045bb4ad1655758","tid":217191,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<br />\n要比多d野食佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法令佢食多d野</blockquote><br />\n放長糧都咁瘦？<br />\n喂開咩糧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F003614_5bdf9f9d943ad16964884b612dcd3a74.jpg&h=99604aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4BC5BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4BC5BD.jpg&h=c337a555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02384Ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02384Ah.jpg&h=c3ac68ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不定期換口味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂喂<br />\n貓既糧唔可以成日換<br />\n我諗你隻貓屙 係因為你咁樣轉糧<br />\n通常係食死一隻 有事/想轉糧先溝糧換<br />\n唔係咁樣一個月 兩個月咁轉黎轉去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一牌子，轉味都唔好？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到佢都覺得慘<br />\n食死一隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食開果隻牌子無事<br />\n正常係可以換口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換牌子穩陣d就溝糧<br />\n<br />\nFussie cat 麻麻地<br />\n我之前有隻食完都成日嘔（唔係我餵）<br />\n換左holistic select 頂住先<br />\n已經無嘔咁多<br />\n+長時間要有乾糧<br />\n+間中餵下雞/魚，就咁煮熟撕開就ok"},{"pid":"12d70e27a6d05bfe560676939cec175836295eb4","tid":217191,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"仲有，嘔完佢應該好快會肚餓<br />\n要提下佢去食多d野"},{"pid":"3538eacfb7dd2f6543fc3db180ae5ee60f39cb31","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有，嘔完佢應該好快會肚餓<br />\n要提下佢去食多d野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，貓貓就係嘔完又沖去食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢無咩膽，唔鍾意嘈，企係門口望下路人，都叫無咁悶既"},{"pid":"69c577bf24655c40b696c7838e9f5cec3a96ca98","tid":217191,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好瘦<br />\n要比多d野食佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法令佢食多d野</blockquote><br />\n放長糧都咁瘦？<br />\n喂開咩糧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/u